    Should Be True    ${NONE VALUE} == None

Scalar String With Escapes
    Should Be Equal    ${ESCAPES}    one \\ two \\\\ \${non_existing}

Empty Scalar String
    Should Be Equal    ${NO VALUE}    ${EMPTY}
