Scalar List
    Should Not Be Equal    ${LIST}    Hello world !
    Should Be True    ${LIST} == ['Hello','again', '?']
    Should Be Equal    ${LIST[0]}    Hello
    Should Be Equal    ${LIST[1]}    again
    Should Be Equal    ${LIST[2]}    ?

Scalar List With Non-Strings
